quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  44,1,Ha. Mim
  44,2,Ka Lengolo le hlakisang lintho tsohle; –
  44,3,"Le rometsoe lefats‘eng bosiung bo hlohonolofetseng: – Hobane Re labalabela ho hlokomelisa(khahlanong le bobe)"
  44,4,Bosiung boo lintho tsohle tsa bohlale lia hlakisoa
  44,5,Ke taelo e tsoang ho Rona – hobane Re lula Re romella (Lits’enolo)
  44,6,E le mohau o tsoang ho Mong`a hau. Hobane U utloa le ho tseba (tsohle)
  44,7,"Mong`a maholimo le lefats’e le tsohle tse lipakeng tsa tsona, haeba le na le tumelo ea ‘nete"
  44,8,"Ha ho `Mopi e mong ntle ho Eena. Ke Eena Ea fanang ka bophelo, ebile U fana ka lefu; – Mong`a le ‘Maballi oa lona le bo-ntat’a lona moholo"
  44,9,Empa feela ba nyanyaka khoaong
  44,10,Joale lebella Letsatsi leo leholimo le tlang ho thunya mosi o bonahalang
  44,11,"O tlang ho aparela batho: sena etla ba Kotlo e mahlonoko"
  44,12,"(Ba tla re): “Mong`a rona! Tlosa kotlo ena holim’a rona, hobane ruri re’a kholoa.”"
  44,13,"Molaetsa o tla ba le matla joang ho bona, empa moromuoa ea neng a hlakisa lintho ka botlalo a se a ile a finyella ho bona, –"
  44,14,"Empa ba ile ba mo furalla, ba re: “O rutiloe, ke lehlanya!”"
  44,15,Re tla fela Re tlose kotlo nakoana e fokolang. Empa ruri ba tla boela litseleng tsa bona
  44,16,"Ka letsatsi le leng Re tla le nanola ka tlhaselo e matla: Ruri! Re tla le Lefisa"
  44,17,"Re ile Ra etsa joalo; pele ho bona, Ra beha sechaba sa Faro tekong: Ho ile ha fihla ho bona Morumuoa ea hlomphehang"
  44,18,"A re: “Ntokolleleng makhabunyane a Allah. Ke moromuoa ea ts’oanelang ho ho ts’eptjoa ho lona"